OL,3,CMore than #21,000 bill for Jersey
OL,4,Cgovernment awards ceremony
OL,6,FIt's been revealed that an annual
OL,7,Fawards ceremony for Jersey's
OL,8,Fgovernment employees cost a third of
OL,9,Fwhat it did in 2023.
OL,11,FA Freedom of Information request
OL,12,Fdisclosed that the government's 'Our
OL,13,FStars Awards' for 2024 cost #21,343.04
OL,14,Fin total.
OL,16,FThat's compared to around #66,000
OL,17,Fspent in the previous year.
