OL,3,CMore than #21,000 bill for Jersey
OL,4,Cgovernment awards ceremony
OL,6,FThe ceremony is held to recognise
OL,7,Fgovernment employees, with the
OL,8,Fgovernment describing it as a way to
OL,9,Fcelebrate the achievements of
OL,10,F"dedicated public servants".
OL,12,FHowever, Jersey's government was
OL,13,Fbranded as "operating in a parallel
OL,14,Funiverse" for using such hefty sums of
OL,15,Ftaxpayers' money to fund the event in
OL,16,Fthe past.
