OL,3,CMore than #21,000 bill for Jersey
OL,4,Cgovernment awards ceremony
OL,6,FConstable Andy Jehan defended the
OL,7,Fspending at the time, saying: "It's
OL,8,Fvital, just as any other employer
OL,9,Fdoes, that you recognise your
OL,10,Fworkforce and particularly those who
OL,11,Fhave made an extra effort."
OL,13,FHe added that the government had
OL,14,F"reined back on the expenses" for the
OL,15,F2023 awards ceremony.
